					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Good luck doing anything like that if you're emulating a Game Boy and a Super Game Boy 2 linked together. Both Game Boy systems are running at a nominal 59.73 Hz, thanks in part to the second oscillator in the SGB2, but the SGB2 has to upconvert that to 60.10 Hz for display.</div>

